From: Jakub Sitnicki <jakub@cloudflare.com>
Date: Thu, 12 Dec 2019 11:22:56 +0100
Subject: selftests/bpf: Propagate errors during setup for reuseport tests
Patch-mainline: v5.6-rc1
Git-commit: 9af6c84435d0252e532c7f8bb70f1ed64a22ae2a
